; a clump of galaxies, which is aligned with the\nlocal large-scale structure and was accreted soon after the formation of the\ncore; and a group of galaxies that fell in more recently.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jun 2019 16:00:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-17"}
