archical triple. The combination of tidal\nsynchronisation and magnetic braking is expected to drive ongoing decay of the\nbrown dwarf orbit, with a remaining lifetime of only 5-10 Myr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jun 2019 16:50:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Sep 2019 10:30:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
