ent with expectations based on the Standard\nModel and with a previous LHCb analysis of this decay using data recorded at\ncentre-of-mass energies 7 and 8 TeV. Finally, the results are combined with\nrecent results from $B^{0}_{s}\\to J/\\psi \\pi^{+} \\pi^{-}$ decays obtained using\nthe same dataset as this analysis, and with previous independent LHCb results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jun 2019 21:08:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Aug 2019 10:56:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2019 12:34:55 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 19 Mar 2020 11:55:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-20"}
