vere, when they had higher education or if they\nhad recently experienced a serious medical condition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 11:20:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 Nov 2019 20:09:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 22 Mar 2020 07:18:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-24"}
